01:19.045 --> 01:21.928
actually, except they didn't come into play until 
I served as student vice president, but there were

01:22.313 --> 01:36.254
some things in place that encouraged 
cross-pollinization between and amongst those

01:22.313 --> 01:36.254
organizations. You know, they've got, oh, I heard 
somebody mention that there are like 20,000

01:37.616 --> 01:45.347
different leadership opportunities or whatever 
