when I initially started in the fall of 1973, I 
lived on campus, as I had done that summer session

13:08.893 --> 13:23.291
before when I lived in McInnis.

13:26.095 --> 13:32.683
And then I dropped out for a year, and because of 
sort of the way I sort of got back into school the

13:33.068 --> 13:35.410
fall of 74. I lived off campus with some friends in 
